name: Shiny Disco Balls Bracelet
description:
This beautifully fun and eye-catching bracelet was a joy to create so it would be a joy to wear this summer!

	Comprises of large Japanese Acrylic Coloured Beads, Czech Glass Beads and a Juicy looking Lucite Strawberry finished off with a spangly Swarovski Heart

	Made to capture the spirit of youthful girly sparkle…..go on give in to your childish self!!!

	(For more pics of this item refer to my myspace)

	xx As with everything, i wouldn’t bother doing it if it wasnt done properly and to the best that i can do xx
